M|ui|```
M|ui|components/
M|ui|├── ui/          # Primitive, reusable (Button, Input, Card)
M|ui|├── features/    # Feature-specific compositions
M|ui|└── layout/      # Page structure (Header, Sidebar, Footer)
M|ui|```
M|ui|- One component per file — no multi-export component files
M|ui|- Props interface defined above the component, exported
M|ui|- Default props via destructuring defaults, not defaultProps
M|ui|- No business logic in UI components — pass data and handlers as props
M|ui|- PascalCase for component files and function names
M|ui|- Props interface: `[ComponentName]Props`
M|ui|- Event handlers: `onXxx` (e.g., `onSubmit`, `onChange`)
M|ui|- Max 80 lines per component
M|ui|- If it exceeds: extract sub-components or move logic to a hook